          "   This pack teaches you to see inside",
          "   English words.",
          "",
          "   Most long English words are built from",
          "   Latin parts: a prefix, a root, and a",
          "   suffix. Learn the parts and you can",
          "   unlock words you have never seen before.",
          "",
          "   You are not memorising a list.",
          "   You are learning a system.",
          "",
          "   Start here. The roots are visible. By",
          "   the end, you will find them hiding in",
          "   places you never expected."
